      "writtenOn": "2026-03-24T01:24:19Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "We could use a \"sizing\" trait or a more flexible template structure:\n\n```cpp\ntemplate \u003ctypename Function, typename... Args\u003e\nclass TinySolver {\n  // Use helper to extract MaxRes, MaxParams, and LinearSolver from Args...\n};\n\n```\nI can look into this if you think this is acceptable.",
